  "title": "Rich Umami Malaysian Mushroom Biryani",
  "description": "A satvik-friendly Malaysian dish featuring marsala wine and dashi extract, cooked in a donabe vessel to create a glassy-jelly texture, evoking nostalgic feelings with its umami flavor.",
