  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in the donabe vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until they release their moisture and start to brown.",
    "Add the marsala wine and dashi extract, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the basmati rice and stir to coat the rice with the mushroom mixture.",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover the donabe vessel, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Turn off the heat and let it rest for 5 minutes before serving."
  ],
